title: Step2 Garden Fresh Kitchen
description: Bring the freshness of your very own “garden” indoors for your little ones with the Step2 Garden Fresh Kitchen!

asset.author: Step2
asset.description:
Bring the freshness of your very own “garden” indoors for your little ones with the Step2 Garden Fresh Kitchen!

To learn more about the Garden Fresh Kitchen, please click here: http://www.step2.com/p/Garden-Fresh-Kitchen

transcripts: watch your little one seeds of imagination grow in this compact kitchen full of surprises and playtime fun. Budding green thumbs can work side by side and plant their own veggies then cut the removable stem off with the play chopping knife after prepping their food junior chefs can sauté their grup on this sizzlin stove burner then turn up the heat with the clicking knob on the stovetop adding to the fun sensory play. Once they're delicious dinner has been gobbled up little chefs can clean up by using the working spray nozzle to wash their dirty dishes. How does your garden grow with the spray nozzle to water the plants and watch they sprout by putting the stems back on. This fresh flavored kitchen comes with plenty of accessories and offers tons of storage in the oven and fridge when cooking time fun is done. The terrifically trendy colors of this kitchen make it right at home in any decor made in the USA with some important parts this kitchen will encourage many gardeners to create healthy habits for years to come. The garden fresh kitchen by step2.
